title: Make It To Me
body:
read it on the AO3 at https://ift.tt/2uMflu4

by Sunshinehina

They were giving up.

Clutching his chest because his heart was hurting so bad, both from their pain and his pain, Tony didn’t even try to blink the tears away.

With everything he got—God knows he did it with everything he got—he sent them one last thought.

‘Make it to me.’

summary: bucky + catching the reader jamming out to ‘breakup with your girlfriend, I’m bored’ by ariana grande and finding it really cute...
question: bucky + catching the reader jamming out to ‘breakup with your girlfriend, I’m bored’ by ariana grande and finding it really cute and hot and it ends in fluffy goodness? I love your writing sm 🥰
answer:
I LIVE FOR SOFT!BUCKY

Bucky could hear the music ever as he was just approaching his apartment.

His elderly neighbour from across the hall had her head poked out of her apartment door and looked at Bucky as he approached her. He was holding his shopping in one hand and his apartment keys in the other and he smiled at Mrs Robinson.

“Hi, ma’am,”

“Your girlfriend’s in an awfully good mood today, James,” she commented, though her face was soft and almost affectionate, not at all annoyed with the ruckus Y/N was making.

“Sorry, ma’am, I’ll turn it down when I get in there,” he promised but Mrs Robinson shook her head, a light smile on her face.

“It’s nice to hear her so happy,” 

“I’ll let her know you said hello, ma’am,” Bucky grinned, sliding his key into his lock and opening the door wide.

“Break up with your girlfriend

Yeah, yeah, ‘cause I’m bored” Y/N sang along to the song loudly, dancing around the kitchen with her university notes held out in front of her. Bucky stopped in the doorway, grinning at her antics, feeling himself falling even further in love with her ever second that he spent with her.

“I think I’ll stick with my girlfriend, thanks,” Bucky teased. Y/N spun around, her face lighting up and she launched herself towards him, chucking her revision to the sides so that she could hug him.

“I missed you!” She giggled and Bucky chuckled, gently brushing her hair out of her face.

“I was gone for under an hour,” Y/N shrugged and moved up onto her toes to kiss him quickly.

“I missed you anyway,” she declared. “But I am glad that you’re not planning on breaking up with your girlfriend,” she teased, kissing him again.

“I wouldn’t dream of it,”
